terrapeer.vui.zone
Class Settlement

java.lang.Object
  terrapeer.vui.zone.Settlement
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Settlement
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

The Settlement class manages a Zone's virtual settlement status. The following lists the property variables. State: SETTLE_NONE SETTLE_RESERVED SETTLE_MOVED SETTLE_SHARED SETTLE_SETTLED Dates: Last time Build Zone Last time Reserved Zone Last time Moved Zone Last time Settled Zone Last time Shared Zone A Move counter - to calculate settlement priorities for frequent moved Zones, i.e. unsuccessful reservations

Title: TerraPeer

Description: P2P feedback system
